<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 04:15:34 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>循环向下箭头</title><link>https://some.pics/69eaee6416c30</link><description>&lt;p&gt;好的，请提供您需要翻译的英文内容。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A small black and white dog lies on her back  in her dog bed with her head and one leg hanging over the side and her her other legs at odd angles." height="1411" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jinx/69eaee6416c30.jpg" width="1881"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jinx.some.pics"&gt;@jinx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 04:15:34 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>机场停机坪上的双螺旋桨飞机</title><link>https://some.pics/69ead455be8ee</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一架小型双螺旋桨飞机停在机场停机坪上，附近有穿着橙色背心的地勤人员，飞机旁边停着设备推车，天空多云。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A small twin-propeller airplane parked on an airport tarmac, with ground crew in orange vests nearby and equipment carts beside the aircraft under a cloudy sky." height="1232" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/davidallen/69ead455be8ee.jpg" width="2128"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://davidallen.some.pics"&gt;@davidallen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 02:24:24 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>飞机着陆时的驾驶舱视角</title><link>https://some.pics/69ead414cd690</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从一架小型飞机驾驶舱内部看到的降落进近景象，飞行员佩戴耳机，手握头顶控制装置，透过挡风玻璃可以看到前方的跑道和蓝绿色海岸线。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="View from inside a small airplane cockpit during landing approach, with a pilot wearing a headset gripping an overhead control while a runway and turquoise coastline are visible ahead through the windshield." height="1232" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/davidallen/69ead414cd690.jpg" width="2128"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://davidallen.some.pics"&gt;@davidallen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 02:23:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>俯瞰热带海岛与碧蓝浅滩</title><link>https://some.pics/69ead37407632</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从小型飞机上俯瞰一座狭长的热带岛屿，碧绿浅水区、沙洲和零星沿海建筑散布其间，两侧被深蓝色海洋环绕。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Aerial view from a small airplane of a long, narrow tropical island with turquoise shallow waters, sandbars, and scattered coastal buildings, surrounded by deeper blue ocean on both sides." height="1232" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/davidallen/69ead37407632.jpg" width="2128"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://davidallen.some.pics"&gt;@davidallen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 02:20:38 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>汉堡和薯条</title><link>https://some.pics/69ead14aa4a8b</link><description>&lt;p&gt;汉堡和薯条&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A double cheeseburger and fries sit on a metal tray." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/69ead14aa4a8b.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 02:11:31 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>